reviewText: ...Natalie Jimenez has one of the greatest voices in ANY musical medium, & with her fellow compadres puts on an enlightening & musically sound unplugged accoustic version of their recorded music with video extras of their first hits...this is an endearing musical set showcasing their superb playing & writing abilities...even if your espanol is poquito-poquito like mine you will immensely enjoy this very talented band!!!
